# phoneNum [! [Version][version-badge][version-lin] ![MIT License][license-badge]]

Display company infomation based on its phone number

### Usage

'''
usage: phone [-h]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help 	show this help message and exit

'''


### Install

'''
$ pip install phoneNum
'''
